@startuml
title OAuth-style login

actor User
participant App
participant Auth
database DB

User -> App : open page
App -> Auth : redirect /authorize
Auth -> User : show login form
User -> Auth : credentials
Auth -> DB : verify
DB --> Auth : ok
Auth --> App : code
App -> Auth : exchange code
Auth --> App : access_token

note over App, Auth
  token cached
  for 1h
end note

alt token valid
  App -> User : show dashboard
else token expired
  App -> Auth : refresh
end
@enduml
